data.description:
*ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 2.75%!* Welcome to your dream home in the highly coveted Hammock Bay community! This spacious and beautifully appointed 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort.With 2,646 square feet of living space on an oversized lot, you'll have room to spread out and enjoy the large backyard, complete with a 600 square foot custom covered patio. Inside, the home boasts quartz countertops, LVP flooring in common and wet areas, elegant shiplap features and plantation shutters throughout. The open-concept living area features vaulted ceilings, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. There is a spacious dining room for the entire family to eat. The versatility of the office/den room allows for easy conversion into an additional bedroom. The sliding barn doors lead to the back patio, a tranquil space for relaxation and entertainment. Beyond your doorstep, the Hammock Bay community provides an array of amenities, including pools, tennis courts, basketball courts, pickleball courts, a micro-brewery, general store, clubhouse, movie theater room, dog park, walking trails, sports fields, and the soon-to-be-completed Freeport Middle School.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite house your forever home. Embrace the lifestyle you deserve in this beautiful, family-friendly neighborhood.
